Okay this is gonna be long but i need someone to talk to. I’m new here so hi guys :). Anyways

Me and this girl, let’s name her K, met eachother 5 months ago, we became great friends almost instantly. K had a boyfriend, who was also her first love, but they were going through problems at the time and I gave her all the attention she needed. She started to get feelings for me and so did I, we became really close and she was basically cheating on her bf with me. After they break up, Me and her just become this cute ass couple but we didn’t date yet. She obviously still has feelings for him around this time and i was fine with that because i understood that, but she had to stop talking to him so she could lose those feelings. Time moves on and i want to be official and date her, she says no everytime and starts to tell me we should stop talking before she hurts me. I ignore it because i can’t just leave her like that. This whole time i’m really falling in love, she made me feel happy, especially coming off of the most depressing time in my life the month before we met. Anyways, two days ago, out of the blue, K tells me she has to tell her ex she cheated on him because she feels really really guilty. I say that’s cool whatever, but after she tells him and they are over that, she asks him “Would you ever want to work it out.” 

She told me she said that, then the next day told me we should stop talking, and i saw them together on campus. She literally went from me to him in one day. She swears that she isn’t getting back with him and that she thinks we shouldn’t talk so she doesn’t hurt me when she ends up going back to him. That hurt. So now everyone is asking how me and K are and i tell them exactly what happened. Then i hear from the grapevine that she’s telling people i “Shouldve known” she was gonna go back to him. After that, i had enough, and told everyone that asked exactly what happened and that she left me to get back with him. 

Later on in the day, she calls me and tells me “Me and my ex aren’t getting back together, i didn’t say that you should’ve known i was gonna go back to him, my business is out in the whole school now because you couldn’t keep your mouth shut with shit i trusted you with.” On top of that, people are calling her a slut, hoe, bitch, all of those. Now i feel like shit and i feel bad because these people are harassing her and it’s my fault. But at the same time I’m so pissed at her for really breaking my heart. I miss her a wholeeeee lot, and now idek what to do. 

I’m so sorry this shit is so long, this whole thing happened literally 2 hours ago so i’m sorry if it’s all over the place i’m still trying to recover. I haven’t ate anything today and i’ve thought about uh a lot of shit i shouldn’t of.
